message.body: Hey lindsey! So we're gathering counts for the centre bridge inn...what do you and your assistant want for dinner? There's braised white beans (vegan), filet mignon, and chicken with creamy mushrooms
2 filet mignon :) thanks lovie! How's plans going?

Excellent! It's going well, I just feel like all these last minute things keep popping up and all the details come together in the last couple weeks...as I'm sure you experienced! Staying sane though! :-)
Haha yeah definitely! Just know it all comes together in the end :-)
True! And no matter what we get to get married :-)
The little things you won't even notice the day of
Like a cicada swarm? Hahaha that's my only concern...
Lol why would you worry about that? Haha
